PrecisRe-appointment of SAM MURDOCK, of Koostatak, Manitoba, as Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months; and approval of the authorization by the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation of SAM MURDOCK to act as President of the Corporation for a period ending October 31, 1999 or until such time as a President is appointed, effective October 24, 1999.
Attachments
precis:
Re-appointment of SAM MURDOCK, of Koostatak, Manitoba, as Chairman of the
Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation to hold
office during pleasure for a term of six months; and approval of the
authorization by the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing
Corporation of SAM MURDOCK to act as President of the Corporation for a
period ending October 31, 1999 or until such time as a President is
appointed, effective October 24, 1999.
